By Mashine MilimoPresident Magufuli s desire to make education free, Education cabinet minister banned state schools from collecting any contributions from parents and guardians. This is a big relief to parents who had to part with about $100 as school fees. The survey indicates that this is President Magufuli s biggest achievement so far.Despite achievement on education being rated the best, the citizenry would like to see more done on education. Other areas to focus on include Health, Employment, Economic growth and agriculture